Hallie Eisenberg https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hallie_Eisenberg 0 Hallie Kate Eisenberg (born August 2, 1992) is an American actress, best known for being "The Pepsi Girl" in a series of Pepsi commercials and her role as Erika Tansy in How to Eat Fried Worms.
